The paper deals with face recognition, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed algorithm is based on a sparse representation framework, which is a popular technique in machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also introduces a new technique for learning and transferring illumination information, which involves optimization and modeling (cs.AI). The experiments involve image processing and analysis, which is a common topic in multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper deals with recognition and retrieval of images, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR).
